<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，你抬頭看看！<delay frames="40" />
滿天星星裡竟然還有流星！<delay20 />
今晚的天空真特別啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">話說流星啊……<delay8 />
其實好像是<delay8 />小得跟沙粒一樣的宇宙塵埃
燃燒過後的產物喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼漂亮的東西竟然是塵埃？<delay20 />
真是不敢相信啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />是流星！！<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可惡～<delay8 />它跑太快了，<delay20 />
害我都沒辦法好好許願啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你快看，<delay8 />這道彩虹！<delay frames="40" />
實在超漂亮的，讓人覺得
剛剛的鬱悶天氣<delay8 />根本不算什麼咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<delay8 />彩虹出現啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能看到象徵好兆頭的東西，<delay8 />
有種賺到的感覺咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說彩虹的盡頭……<delay8 />不知道是什麼樣子啊？<delay frames="40" />
就算一次也好，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真想靠近點看啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到<delay8 />我竟然有緣見到雙彩虹啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛剛的鬱悶天氣<delay8 />
根本一點都不算什麼啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原本天氣還陰沉得很，<delay20 />
意外就讓人看到了大飽眼福的美景啊！<delay frames="40" />
這下總覺得會發生什麼好事咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這傢伙真是驚人啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是有彩虹出現就已經很少見了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果今天的彩虹竟然還是兩道！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，<delay8 />你不覺得極光……<delay20 />
看起來很像光的窗簾嗎？<delay frames="40" />
而且只要伸出手，感覺就碰得到咧！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是把它掀開，不知道會怎麼樣啊？<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />不過就是普通的夜空吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是讓人目瞪口呆的光景啊！<delay frames="40" />
看著這麼漂亮的極光，<delay20 />
我的力量就湧了上來咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天啊～！<delay20 />這極光真漂亮！<delay frames="40" />
我冒著寒冷出門<delay8 />真是值得啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要是<delay8 />有一大堆飛機在空中盤旋，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天空不就<delay8 />一下子都是雲啦！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天啊～！<delay20 />我可不想要這樣咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我每次看到飛機雲都會這麼想<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />要是把天空跟雲用在新年第一次寫書法，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不覺得這樣……
新年就會很動感嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飛機雲的痕跡真清楚<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
說不定這表示<delay8 />
天氣馬上就要變差啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我問你，<delay8 />有沒有人跟你說過
「今晚月亮真漂亮」<delay8 />這句話啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這句台詞啊，<delay8 />好像是以前哪個浪漫傢伙想的，
是用來告白的話咧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />這件事跟我無緣就是啦！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的月亮啊，<delay20 />
都是用表面示人咧！<delay frames="40" />
要說月亮的背面……<delay8 />你應該也沒看過吧？
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想要像這月亮一樣，<delay8 />
活得表裡如一咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果一直抬頭看著天空，<delay20 />
脖子就會開始痛起來<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過這樣的滿月<delay8 />真叫人看得入迷咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>